%% Diagram: ISR cache lifecycle
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Built: build time prerender
    Built --> Fresh: deploy to CDN
    Fresh --> Fresh: request within revalidate window
    Fresh --> Stale: revalidate window expires
    Stale --> Regenerating: first request after expiry\n(returns stale to caller)
    Regenerating --> Fresh: regenerated HTML\nreplaces cache
    Regenerating --> Stale: regeneration error\n(serve stale, retry next request)

    Fresh --> Regenerating: revalidatePath / revalidateTag\n(on-demand)
    note right of Stale
        Caller still gets a fast
        cached response while a
        background re-render runs.
    end note
